item.title: Omg Help Me!
item.dc:creator: @pmgz2 pmgz2
item.description:
@pmgz2 wrote:

Umm, sure i can explain.

} else if (NPCID == NPCID) { PutNPCCoords = true; WanneShop = WANNESHOP# HERE.;

you should put this under:

something close or similar to this:

} else if (NPCID == 300 || NPCID == 844 || NPCID == 462) { /*Essence Mine Guys*/ teleportToX = 3088; teleportToY = 3489; if (NPCID == 300) { Essence = 1; } else if (NPCID == 844) { Essence = 2; } else if (NPCID == 462) { Essence = 3; }

Ok. you can’t open .Cfg, do this.

right click a .cfg file and find open with… then click notepad. and then you can see it, make sure to tick the box that says always use this answer for these types of files, or something similar to that, i can’t rememeber.

once your in shops.cfg make sure to add use tabs

for example:

shop = 1	@whi@Barrows_Shop@whi@				1	1

TABBING is essential, if you do not tab you will get errors, and you will be disconnected when you try to log in, OR not even be able to log in at all, so please becareful.

I hope i helped you.

and Np about the first problem you had =)
im Glad to help.
